_sText:
**2012 25 January** _Swedish salvage divers discovered an unexplained object resting at the bottom of the Baltic Sea._
**2012 on April 4.** _Three countries: Russia, Lithuania and Estonia organized NIIBNO._
**2012 on April 28.** _Construction of underwater station round unknown object began._
**2012 on July 27.** _Scientists from all countries for BNO studying are brought together._
**2012 on November 13.** _Scientists forward on underwater station._
**2013 on January 11.** _Suspicious vessels in BNO place are noticed._
**2013 on January 15.** _The vessel was destroyed, on it there was a set of explosive._
**2013 on January 16.** _It is decided to make an ambush for destruction of terrorists._
**2013 on May 1.** _Terrorists got on underwater station..._
